BEGIN_TEXT
Let
\[ f(x) = \frac{$a x^3 - $b x^2}{\sqrt[3]{x^{$c}}}. \]
Evaluate \( f'(x) \) at the indicated point:
$PAR
\( f'($r1)\) = \{ans_rule(40) \}
END_TEXT

